long_description: sportees got its start in canada's yukon over 40 years ago with a line of custom clothing tailored to fit the active lifestyles of outdoor and fitness enthusiasts. from the quality of our fabrics to our meticulous workmanship, sportees garments are designed for comfort and built to last. sportees combines performance fabrics with high quality construction – without the high price. running and rock climbing. you'll find us indoors too, from the fitness gym to the dance recital. plus sportees active wear can double as rugged work wear or everyday active wear for 'casual friday' at the office, running the kids to soccer practice or just sporting around town. we've made clothing for the fulda tire company's media contingent in the yukon quest, wind suits for the canadian orienteering team at world championships, vests and hats for the yukon ski team, and kitted out numerous teams at the arctic winter games. it's vital to us that we support our local community. whether you're ordering for yourself or your whole team, with sportees it's not just about the great outdoors…it's about all the great gear that goes with it.
